 FileName   Lrecl  Records   Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ReadMe         80        .   This file
table3.dat     82       57   Recommended Atomic transition probabilities for
                             Mn I (half integral J) & Mn II (integral J)
                             organized by increasing wavelength in air
table4.dat     52      753  *Hyperfine structure line component patterns
                             for ^55^MnI (integral F) & ^55^MnII
                             (half integral F)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note on table4.dat : organized by increasing wavelength in air, lamAir;
  computed using published Hyperfine structure (hfs) constants, energy levels
  from Sugar & Corliss (1985, J. Phys. Chem. Ref. Data, 14, 338), and the
  standard index of air (Peck & Reeder 1972JOSA...62..958P).
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See also:
   VI/34 : A Multiplet Table for MnI (Adelman+, 1989)
   J/A+AS/125/539 : Mn III transition probabilities (Uylings+ 1997)

